</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans antialiased flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-screen">

    <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->
    <nav class="md:w-64 bg-brand-navy text-white flex-shrink-0 md:h-screen md:sticky top-0 shadow-xl z-20">
        <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                <i data-lucide="book-open" class="text-brand-orange w-8 h-8"></i>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold leading-tight">Playbook<br><span class="text-brand-orange">Agence</span></h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 hidden md:block">
                <li><a href="#vision" class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 px-3 rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"><i data-lucide="scale" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i> Vision & Cadre</a></li>
                <li><a href="#gouvernance" class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 px-3 rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"><i data-lucide="users" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i> Gouvernance</a></li>
                <li><a href="#projet" class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 px-3 rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"><i data-lucide="rocket" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i> Méthode Projet</a></li>
                <li><a href="#staffing" class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 px-3 rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"><i data-lucide="briefcase" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i> Staffing & Heures</a></li>
                <li><a href="#quotidien" class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 px-3 rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"><i data-lucide="calendar-clock" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i> Quotidien (TT)</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-x-hidden">
        
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <header class="bg-brand-navy text-white pt-20 pb-24 px-8 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-orange rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
                <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-brand-orange text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide mb-6 border border-brand-orange/30">VERSION USAGE INTERNE</span>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">Playbook Opérationnel <br>& <span class="text-brand-orange">Vie d'Agence</span></h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">Alignement sur les processus, les rôles et les standards d'excellence pour garantir notre efficacité collective.</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 -mt-12 relative z-10 space-y-20">

            <!-- Section 1: Vision -->
            <section id="vision" class="scroll-mt-12">
                <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-brand-orange"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                                <i data-lucide="scale" class="text-brand-orange w-8 h-8"></i>
                                Cadre Clair = Liberté d'Action
                            </h2>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">Plus d'autonomie demande plus de précision. Ce document clarifie les zones grises entre le "Doc Orga" théorique et la réalité du terrain.</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                    <i data-lucide="target" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span><strong>L'objectif est l'efficacité :</strong> réduire les allers-retours inutiles et garantir la qualité de notre production.</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                    <i data-lucide="unlock" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span>Ces règles ne sont pas des freins, mais des <strong>leviers pour garantir votre autonomie</strong> sur les projets.</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2: Gouvernance -->
            <section id="gouvernance" class="scroll-mt-12">
                <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy">La Gouvernance</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Le 'Doc Orga' fait foi en cas de doute sur la hiérarchie ou le circuit de validation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <!-- Julien -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-navy/5 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-navy">
                            <i data-lucide="crown" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Rôle : Julien</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500"></i> Intervention stratégique.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="x" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500"></i> Pas de mise en relation systématique dès la demande.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"></i> Conserve parfois le "Lead Client".</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Simon -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-orange/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand-orange">
                            <i data-lucide="search" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Rôle : Simon</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500"></i> Rôle défini par le Doc Orga.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="x" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500"></i> Intervention / mise en copie non automatique.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"></i> Dépend de la phase du projet (sourcing).</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- CDP -->
                    <div class="bg-brand-navy rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md text-white">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white">
                            <i data-lucide="settings" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Chef de Projet (CDP)</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-orange font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Maître du Processus & Machine Projet</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-4">Création To-Do, Deadlines, Plateforme, Détails.</p>
                        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded p-3 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                            <strong>Note :</strong> Même si un supérieur a le 'Lead Client', le CDP reste propriétaire de l'opérationnel.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Philosophie & Rythme -->
                <div class="mt-6 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-orange-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-orange mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Philosophie 'Estelle'</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">L'autonomie est encouragée (moins de synchronisations, plus d'action), mais jamais au détriment du projet.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="repeat" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Rythme de Synchro Idéal</h4>
                        <ol class="text-sm text-slate-700 list-decimal list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>Avant/Après Sourcing</li>
                            <li>Vérification Propal & Budget</li>
                            <li>Avant Envoi</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3: Méthodologie Projet -->
            <section id="projet" class="scroll-mt-12">
                <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Le Lancement & Le Sourcing</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">La rigueur dès les premières heures définit le succès du projet.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Kickoff Timeline -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-8 mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6 text-center">Le Kick-off : Pas de précipitation</h3>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 relative">
                        <!-- J0 -->
                        <div class="bg-slate-100 w-40 h-40 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-4 border-white shadow-md z-10">
                            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-brand-navy">J0</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">Réception Demande</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Interdit -->
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-red-500 z-10 md:mx-4 my-4 md:my-0">
                            <i data-lucide="ban" class="w-10 h-10 mb-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-center">Pas de Kick-off<br>ce jour-là</span>
                        </div>

                        <!-- J1+ -->
                        <div class="bg-brand-orange text-white w-48 h-48 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-4 border-white shadow-lg z-10">
                            <span class="text-3xl font-black mb-1">J1+</span>
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium opacity-90">Analyse & Préparation</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-5">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Pré-requis avant démarrage (J1+) :</h4>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                            <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-brand-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0">1</span><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Questions envoyées au client.</p></div>
                            <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-brand-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0">2</span><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Rétroplanning défini en amont.</p></div>
                            <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-brand-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0">3</span><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Identification claire du "Lead Client" et des rôles.</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-center text-sm font-medium text-brand-orange mt-5 bg-brand-orange/10 py-2 rounded">
                            Pourquoi ? Il faut laisser le temps nécessaire à Simon pour l'analyse et le pré-sourcing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Entonnoir Sourcing -->
                <div class="bg-brand-navy rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Stratégie de Sourcing : L'Entonnoir de Sélection</h3>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-stretch mb-8 relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center"><i data-lucide="filter" class="text-white"></i></div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-orange mb-2 uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Entrée</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Volume Élevé.<br>Multiplier les demandes !</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-brand-orange"><i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 hidden md:block"></i><i data-lucide="arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 md:hidden"></i></div>
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center"><i data-lucide="minimize-2" class="text-white"></i></div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-orange mb-2 uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Filtrage</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Moins de destinations,<br>forte intensité par destination.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-brand-orange"><i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 hidden md:block"></i><i data-lucide="arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 md:hidden"></i></div>
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-white/10 border border-brand-orange/30 rounded-lg p-6 text-center ring-2 ring-brand-orange/50">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-orange mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-orange/20"><i data-lucide="send" class="text-white"></i></div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-orange mb-2 uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Sortie</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">2 propositions<br>envoyées au client.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-brand-orange/20 border border-brand-orange/30 rounded p-4 text-sm text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="text-brand-orange w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                        <p><strong>PRO TIP :</strong> Le coup de cœur doit rester très exceptionnel. On privilégie la rationalité et le volume de prospection.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 4: Staffing & Heures -->
            <section id="staffing" class="scroll-mt-12">
                <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Staffing Événement & Heures Supp'</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Règles de composition d'équipe et récupération post-événement.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <!-- Composition -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">La Logique d'Attribution</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="text-brand-orange w-4 h-4"></i> Qui a vendu le projet ?</li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="text-brand-orange w-4 h-4"></i> <strong class="text-brand-navy">Qui a travaillé sur la production ? (Prioritaire)</strong></li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Règles de Seniorité</h3>
                        
                        <!-- Bad Config -->
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3 border border-red-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="user" class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-500 mx-auto"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">Junior</span>
                                </div>
                                <i data-lucide="plus" class="text-slate-400"></i>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="graduation-cap" class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-500 mx-auto"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">Stagiaire</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600 font-bold bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded shadow-sm">
                                <i data-lucide="x-circle" class="w-5 h-5"></i> INTERDIT
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Good Config -->
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-green-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <div class="relative inline-block">
                                        <i data-lucide="user" class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-navy mx-auto"></i>
                                        <i data-lucide="glasses" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-navy absolute top-2 right-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-navy block">Senior</span>
                                </div>
                                <i data-lucide="plus" class="text-slate-400"></i>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="users" class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-500 mx-auto"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 block">Junior/Stagiaire</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 font-bold bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded shadow-sm">
                                <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5"></i> OBLIGATOIRE
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-center text-slate-500 mt-3 italic">La présence d'un Senior est obligatoire pour encadrer les profils juniors.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Heures -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-0 overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
                        <div class="bg-brand-navy p-6 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
                                <i data-lucide="clock" class="text-brand-orange"></i> Heures Supplémentaires
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-4">
                            
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
                                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Fin jusqu'à <span class="text-brand-navy font-bold text-lg">00h00</span></span>
                                <span class="text-sm bg-orange-100 text-brand-orange font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Récup : 1/2 journée <span class="font-normal text-xs text-orange-800">(Retour 14h)</span></span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
                                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Fin jusqu'à <span class="text-brand-navy font-bold text-lg">05h00</span></span>
                                <span class="text-sm bg-orange-100 text-brand-orange font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Récup : 1 journée</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
                                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Week-ends & Fériés</span>
                                <span class="text-sm bg-green-100 text-green-700 font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Payés <span class="font-normal text-xs text-green-800">(si vendu client)</span></span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mt-auto pt-4 flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded">
                                <i data-lucide="shield-alert" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                                <p><strong>Validation impérative</strong> à définir avec le chef d'équipe + validation Marie.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 5: Quotidien -->
            <section id="quotidien" class="scroll-mt-12">
                <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Quotidien & Agence</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Politique de télétravail, rythme de travail et hygiène opérationnelle.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- TT Policy -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-8 mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6 text-center">Politique de Télétravail (TT)</h3>
                    
                    <!-- Calendar View -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2 md:gap-4 text-center font-bold text-sm md:text-base mb-8">
                        <div class="bg-brand-navy text-white p-3 md:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-inner flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <span class="opacity-80 text-xs mb-1">LUN</span>
                            <span>BUREAU</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-brand-navy text-white p-3 md:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-inner flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <span class="opacity-80 text-xs mb-1">MAR</span>
                            <span>BUREAU</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-brand-navy text-white p-3 md:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-inner flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <span class="opacity-80 text-xs mb-1">MER</span>
                            <span>BUREAU</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-brand-orange text-white p-3 md:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col justify-center transform scale-105 z-10">
                            <span class="opacity-90 text-xs mb-1">JEU</span>
                            <span class="text-xl">TT</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white text-brand-navy border-2 border-brand-navy border-dashed p-3 md:p-6 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <span class="opacity-60 text-xs mb-1">VEN</span>
                            <span>FLEX</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

